            "value": "<p><span>This wand increases a spellâ€™s duration. Yellow embers spiral over its surface until the spell ends.<br></span></p>\n<p><span><strong>Activate</strong> Cast a Spell; <strong>Frequency</strong> once per day, plus overcharge; the activation takes <span style=\"font-family: 'Pathfinder2eActions'; font-size: 1.8em; display: inline;\">D</span> if the spell normally takes <span style=\"font-family: 'Pathfinder2eActions'; font-size: 1.8em; display: inline;\">A</span> to cast, or <span style=\"font-family: 'Pathfinder2eActions'; font-size: 1.8em; display: inline;\">T</span> if the spell normally takes <span style=\"font-family: 'Pathfinder2eActions'; font-size: 1.8em; display: inline;\">D</span>; <strong>Effect</strong> You Cast the Spell, and its duration is increased by&nbsp;half.<br></span></p>\n<p><span><strong>Craft Requirements</strong> Supply a casting of a spell of the appropriate level. The spell must have a casting time of <span style=\"font-family: 'Pathfinder2eActions'; font-size: 1.8em; display: inline;\">A</span> or <span style=\"font-family: 'Pathfinder2eActions'; font-size: 1.8em; display: inline;\">D</span> and a duration no less than 10 minutes and no greater than 1 hour.</span></p>",
